### ========================================
### Project: "default"
### ========================================

### Add a user to the default project waiting list
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: default

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Add another user to the default project
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: default

{
  "firstname": "Jane",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com"
}

### Get all waiting list entries for the default project
GET http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
X-Project-ID: default

### Look up a user by email in the default project
GET http://localhost:8081/waitinglist/users?email=john.doe@example.com
X-Project-ID: default

