### ========================================
### Error cases
### ========================================

### Duplicate email within the same project (expect 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: beta-app

{
  "firstname": "Alice",
  "lastname": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@example.com"
}

### Same email in a different project (expect 201 Created — emails are scoped per project)
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: internal-tools

{
  "firstname": "Alice",
  "lastname": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@example.com"
}

### Unknown project slug (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: nonexistent-project

{
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "User",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Missing required fields (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: default

{
  "firstname": "",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "missing@example.com"
}

### Invalid email (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json
X-Project-ID: beta-app

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Missing email query param (expect 400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:8081/waitinglist/users
X-Project-ID: default

### ========================================
### Admin — project-scoped queries
### ========================================

### List all projects
GET http://localhost:8081/admin/projects
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

### Dashboard for default project
GET http://localhost:8081/admin/dashboard?project=default
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

### Dashboard for beta-app project
GET http://localhost:8081/admin/dashboard?project=beta-app
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

### Users with access in beta-app
GET http://localhost:8081/admin/users/access?project=beta-app
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

### Waitlist entries for internal-tools
GET http://localhost:8081/admin/users/waitlist?project=internal-tools
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=
